snippet.title: Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed DLC #1 Teaser
snippet.description:
DLC 1 is here and it's FREE! Take a step into the MOROS Medical Facility, if you dare. 
We also hope you have an appetite for a new Ghost Type, cause the Glutton is here! With the Glutton, our old friend Muncher is back!

Get all the details here:
Discord.gg/GhostbustersSU

Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed is available on PC on EPIC GAMES, PS4™, PS4™Pro, PS5™, Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One. To learn more about the game visit: https://www.ghostbusterssu.com/

Want to get the latest news on the game OR to meet up with other players in the community? Join us using these links!

https://discord.gg/ghostbusterssu
